{"tid":1972334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透社：匿名法官指香港司法獨立正受中共攻擊 大陸法官不明白香港出亂象的因由","createTime":"2020-04-14T12:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T12:51:56.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc2e35b1af5b51cb9f0677ebdf3179b1e9e20ed0","tid":1972334,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"路透社匿名引述法官指香港司法獨立正受中共攻擊<br />\n14.04.2020 20:30<br />\n<br />\n路透社匿名引述香港的資深法官指，香港的司法獨立正受到中共攻擊，形容是自1997年以來最大的威脅；報道又引述接近終審法院首席法官馬道立的人士指，馬道立要應對，認為法治最終目的是維持一黨統治的中共官員。報道指，有多名香港法官、律師和外交人員受訪，他們都認為北京正是多管齊下，打擊香港司法制度，官媒警告香港的法官不能赦免去年示威者的罪責，有法官和律師反映，有跡象顯示北京試圖限制香港法院在處理核心憲制問題的權力。<br />\n<br />\n報道又引述有法官指，與內地的法官交流時，對方不明白香港為何出現亂象，而不愛國。有關法官擔心北京正失去耐性，設法加緊控制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280742&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1280742%26csid%3D261_341&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=99fb508a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280742&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5e0efef311610c458cf1b2ff2b945f5ec5db7f68","tid":1972334,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"b51349833a0d841d53402610e3be3b7958286a88","tid":1972334,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15667937cb102209b1462fd2f1ecc75393e995a8","tid":1972334,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:38:59.000Z","msg":"等班法律界咀砲撚瞓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626a830f0a6ab82d3d23487a318e066630772d5c","tid":1972334,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"